{"tid":1686592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"江永祥：警方搗破有人在網上兜售伸縮警棍及電槍等武器","createTime":"2019-11-01T08:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T13:21:00.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f3204c43e66fbcfee58f35d35bc9186fc6b7a8","tid":1686592,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:45:16.000Z","msg":"警方在記者會表示，星期一在屯門不同區域均有報告指聞到不明氣體，<span style=\"color: red;\">重申警方沒有在大興行動基地測試催淚彈</span>。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司謝振中表示，當晚有大批人士在大興行動基地外聚集，指不滿聞到異味，不斷咒罵警方、縱火、堵路等，亦有一批人破壞一間茶餐廳，縱火出現濃煙可能威脅樓上市民，警方共拘捕61人。謝振中形容，事件是體現「無中生有」、暴徒的行為純粹是暴力發洩的破壞，及肆意破壞無辜商店。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到暴徒昨晚打著「萬聖節」的旗號，進行破壞及堵路，又指在旺角有火警，但暴徒阻止消防車駛過，所以警方要進行驅散。他又說，旺角有黑衣暴徒毆打一名男子，包括狂插、圍毆等，男子一度失去知覺，暴徒用懷疑電槍進行攻擊，批評殘暴的心態不能以言語形容。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，昨晚首次發現一批壓縮氣體燃料的爆炸品，雖然當時沒有被燃點，但指燃點後會傷及警員及附近人士。警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥表示，星期一至今共拘捕249人，年齡由13至61歲。<span style=\"color: red;\">另外警方又搗破有人在網上兜售伸縮警棍及電槍等武器</span>，警方今日假扮買家，買到相關武器，拘捕一名男子，已交由重案組跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489534-20191101.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489534-20191101.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=8a8bd487\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489534-20191101.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2551ef22\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489534-20191101.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5791ab2b31969171f930cbb3e5b282c87ca77442","tid":1686592,"uid":268516,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"昨晚首次發現一批壓縮氣體燃料的爆炸品<br />\n<br />\n以後買氣打邊爐都會俾人拉"},{"pid":"48f3a0ba97895e531dfb6b8d8c9684bc4c4b46d5","tid":1686592,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054a03b1bf1e3e346206925931873688d47c7bb1","tid":1686592,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"沒有在大興 即係唔係大興放囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990493810803aa069aa27a01cd42d992d6054fb8","tid":1686592,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:40:29.000Z","msg":"講撚到好似第一日有人賣彈彈咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周街都係啦on9 拉埋大陸個班呀嗎"},{"pid":"ecf6dd32ba19773c39a7e6ffcea0f2850f6f4964","tid":1686592,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"話有人用電槍襲擊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cff18540de9ee395948efda82f7d12c9a6d0637","tid":1686592,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672ef99edc1d86a701ee6457c91a9115010a5ac1","tid":1686592,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqzNguY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqzNguY.png&h=2c0b8080&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}